data.description: This impressive home has ROOM FOR ALL, with 5  bedrooms, and 3 bathrooms! One bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor,  next to the guest bathroom which makes this the perfect space for in-laws or  out-of-town guests. The BONUS ROOM and 3-CAR GARAGE offer TONS OF STORAGE!  Imagine heading home after a long day ... as you enter this upscale, gated community,  the sense of security you feel is comforting. You smile as you drive past the playground  and consider maybe hitting the fitness center or community pool later. Once on Oak  Pond, you feel a sense of pride as you drive up to your beautiful home with amazing  curb appeal! You enter your code in your SMART HOME's front door, stroll past the  formal living and dining room, drop your keys on the GRANITE COUNTERTOP, and grab  a beverage in the stylish kitchen with stainless steel, energy-efficient appliances. You  decide to enjoy your drink on your screened-in lanai, overlooking your HUGE backyard  with CONSERVATION VIEW! Later, back inside, you and the family enjoy dinner and  then watch a movie in the family room before retiring upstairs to your PRIVATE  OWNERS SUITE where you enjoy a soak in the garden tub, before you drift off to  dreamland, ending this perfect day! You sleep well knowing your home is protected with  the HOME WARRANTY the Seller provided for your peace of mind as well as the fact that  your ECOSMART CERTIFIED HOME saves you a lot of money on your utility  bill...PLUS-NEW WINDOWS INSTALLED IN DECEMBER 2023! Hawks Point is located in  the heart of Ruskin, with charming shops, restaurants, and even an old-fashioned  drive-in theater! Easy access to the interstate means you are minutes away from  Tampa, Beaches, and Theme Parks. Call today for your private showing!
